beginning, containing an area of TWENTY SIX THOUSAND EIGHT HUNDRED FIFTY NINE (26,859) SQUARE METERS, more or less. All points referred to are indicated on the plan and are marked on the ground by PLS Conc. Mons. Bearing true; date of the original survey, October, 1936 to July 1940 and that of the subdivision survey, September 12, to November 30, 1952, which was approved on January 16, 1954.

IN WITNESS WHEREOF, I have hereunto set my hand and caused the seal of the Republic of the Philippines to be affixed.

Done in the City of Manila, this 23rd day of November, in the year of Our Lord, nineteen hundred and ninety-two.

(Sgd.) FIDEL V. RAMOS

By the President: (Sgd.) EDELMIRO A. AMANTE, SR. Executive Secretary

